VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT struts\.enable\.DynamicMethodInvocation\s*=\s*true|<constant\s+name="struts\.enable\.DynamicMethodInvocation"\s+value="true"
WHEN EXPR MISSING:SecurityMemberAccess|OgnlContextState|allowlist|xwork\.security\.excludedClasses
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Struts configuration with Dynamic Method Invocation (DMI) enabled.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Dynamic Method Invocation Enabled.
